comment: Lemma for ~ cvmlift . The ` Q ( M ) ` functions are defined on almost disjoint intervals, but they overlap at the edges. Here we show that at these points the ` Q ` functions agree on their common domain. (Contributed by Mario Carneiro, 14-Feb-2015.)
